1773601276384178	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3tQs		item.create	bn-37wc	{"description":"detail_lines() is called redundantly — once in max_detail_scroll() (every clamp_detail_scroll call), once in render_detail_panel() (every frame at 10fps). Cache the Vec<Line> result in ListView and invalidate only when detail_item changes. Measured: 65µs per call, 10+ calls/sec = wasted CPU.","kind":"task","title":"cache detail_lines() output in TUI"}	blake3:fPORII9Awu59mZy1joc9ZlYVeqtLUllgs6tJ2ZcKXVA
1773601279053424	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3tgs		item.create	bn-3k2t	{"description":"refresh_selected_detail() at list.rs:3405 reloads the full detail (including all comments from SQLite) every 2 seconds even when the same bone is selected and nothing has changed. Add a staleness check using updated_at_us from the DB before reloading. Measured: load_detail_item takes 304µs per call with 15 comments.","kind":"task","title":"skip detail reload when bone unchanged"}	blake3:EsA-NuQebFheRNakqHcqT9nOe0FYZqmL_JGgZtlvAXU
1773601281823302	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3tws		item.create	bn-2ed6	{"description":"get_comments() in load_detail_item (list.rs:3469) is called with None, None — loading ALL comments for the selected bone. Pass a reasonable limit (e.g. 200 most recent). The query layer already supports limit/offset params. Agent progress comments are low-value in the TUI detail pane.","kind":"task","title":"add comment limit to TUI detail pane"}	blake3:n6XY0rrfcVmRYDdtc5Upg0YPcbL4TdF7ourKyPsDpFM
1773601285480079	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE3uAs		item.create	bn-2rbf	{"description":"Add optional DHAT or jemalloc profiling support behind a feature flag so we can measure allocation patterns in bn ui during real usage. When the 1.6GB RSS issue recurs, we need to be able to capture a heap profile. Consider: dhat-rs behind a 'dhat' feature, jemalloc with profiling behind a 'jemalloc' feature, or tikv-jemallocator with MALLOC_CONF for heap dumps.","kind":"task","title":"add debug allocator support for bn ui memory profiling"}	blake3:K6zfi6gcxT18Hg_zDJQcYQmvo64pTApsVRDT6lIm5lA
