1774190898284673	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE31ws		item.create	bn-1dhm	{"description":"The semantic-ort feature pulls in ort (ONNX Runtime) which causes CRT linking conflicts on Windows (MD_DynamicRelease vs MT_StaticRelease from esaxx-rs). Make semantic-ort a feature flag on bones-cli, keeping it in defaults so Linux/macOS behavior is unchanged but Windows users can build with --no-default-features --features otel. Ref: https://github.com/SubliminalCoding/Bones-Windows-Fork","kind":"task","labels":["platform"],"title":"Windows support: make semantic-ort opt-in feature"}	blake3:iPMfqpTKAtTt7pJdOyDxGmWDX3dHzym0dLikunfZNkU
1774191170870234	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE32As		item.create	bn-j8vp	{"description":"Add model2vec (safetensors + tokenizers, no ONNX) as an alternative embedding backend in bones-search. This avoids the CRT linking conflict on Windows while still providing real semantic embeddings. Feature-gate as semantic-model2vec. Ref: frankensearch-embed's approach.","kind":"task","labels":["platform","search"],"title":"Add model2vec embedding backend for Windows-friendly semantic search"}	blake3:Xz6q0alQSznC6ffVJFduw8w9DLnNS7Ez8mHTNSyeQQQ
