1774201369546006	bones-dev	itc:v3:AWKSZJkkk5JkmZMxAAAAQatWqrq1bWwAAAE36ws		item.create	bn-22nk	{"description":"MIN_SEMANTIC_SCORE (0.60) and MIN_SEMANTIC_TOP_SCORE_NO_LEXICAL (0.62) in hybrid search are too aggressive. When FTS5 returns nothing (e.g. 'authentication' vs 'auth'), semantic results are discarded even though they're relevant. This defeats the purpose of semantic search as a fuzzy bridge. Also add --semantic-threshold CLI flag to bn search for experimentation.","kind":"task","labels":["search"],"title":"Loosen semantic search score thresholds for better recall"}	blake3:93qJbvul1nSaFpjYKDQDjNQhszTbdXPyIZ4buKWo3Sk
